{"tid":196280,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"法律巴絲幫幫手，屋企人被人打 仲比人告","createTime":"2017-04-11T07:43:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T10:48:02.000Z","uid":105430,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f93c1e91a602f76dd24387d604230722e2c2ff34","tid":196280,"uid":105430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T07:43:02.000Z","msg":"我媽係售貨員,五十幾歲<br />\n另一女店員因長期睇我媽唔順眼,<br />\n有一日老闆講左個女店員幾句,<br />\n女店員懷疑係我媽唱衰佢,叫左我媽埋一邊話傾兩句<br />\n之後就向我媽動武,<br />\n左手一巴掌向我媽臉部, 被我媽擋左一下<br />\n之後再手拉住我媽,我媽用手大力fing開佢<br />\n佢再申腳,我媽跌地 手指骨折<br />\n最後 報call左白車 報左警 落左口供 <br />\n對方完全無事，下午已如常開工<br />\n<br />\n有cctv 錄左 ,因為我媽有用手擋同大力fing開佢<br />\n警方呢家告雙方 公眾地方打鬥<br />\n店長話咩都見唔到 唔做證人<br />\n我媽怕事話唔想打官司 話之後上法院認罪就算<br />\n我應該點做？有無法律巴打可以幫幫手<br />\n唔想我媽咁樣含冤受屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03a1ca022fde246e69feafed24eda9b215a8788","tid":196280,"uid":1444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T07:48:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f1863b21b5849926702bf6acd021bec04d7494a","tid":196280,"uid":40996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T07:50:16.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"d12bfc41d15e867b5e8c00527344786dc38468f4","tid":196280,"uid":36696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T07:52:40.000Z","msg":"幾時提堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cac756872ce3b2d2bfa440d69bb61d1f8173ae5","tid":196280,"uid":25099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T07:52:50.000Z","msg":"咁都唔係自衛?"},{"pid":"99fdd993c26a58e95ea0f16924b7e479bbabfc2d","tid":196280,"uid":105430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T07:53:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾時提堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n4月21號"},{"pid":"d25bd1fc605dfb498e7b132447434bf640c0a40b","tid":196280,"uid":105430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T07:54:0