 />\n我應該點做？有無法律巴打可以幫幫手<br />\n唔想我媽咁樣含冤受屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 不過你媽宜家傷 又有cctv 見到自衞<br />\n入罪機會不大呀<br />\n問下律師啦!!!"},{"pid":"444a49c1bff4103432603704bafb97dae3d8bca0","tid":196280,"uid":3846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T07:59:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾時提堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n4月21號</blockquote><br />\n搵當值律師幫手，唔知$460定$500</blockquote><br />\n當值律師都係幫手求情多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0008968a6ad2ac5ed6381c9a86b182b4f4c5f6","tid":196280,"uid":36696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T08:00:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾時提堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n4月21號</blockquote><br />\n搵當值律師幫手，唔知$460定$500</blockquote><br />\n當值律師都係幫手求情多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n理論上嚟講，嗰位律師係跟你嘅指示行事"},{"pid":"e4a39996ea3ee5543fc89e465d0c63a5210ae513","tid":196280,"uid":17159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T08:01:45.000Z","msg":"拉應該同對家口供有關 律政出legal advise比驚提告<br />\n但係告唔告得入就睇打程序同證據 既然有cctv影到<br />\n咪比佢審下 冇做就冇做 比我會情願個官判錯我都唔會認罪<br />\n利申 鳩up"},{"pid":"c3006f801ac47c9021b5075ea64e6f234984a2ff","tid":196280,"uid":105430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T08:07:47.000Z","msg":"因為我媽好怕事,所以 我想知我呢家應該點處理, 除左交哂比律師做 仲有無咩可以做到？"},{"pid":"892781c9a99754f88e716fea90863f84dc946ff5","tid":196280,"uid":2545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T08:09:04.000Z","msg":"利申我唔係讀law<br />\n但我老豆早兩年都係街同人打交<br />\n我老豆比人打, 打到豬頭咁, 打佢個阿叔就咩傷都冇<br />\n跟住又係2個都比警察告公眾地方打鬥<br />\n果陣去完醫院驗傷, 又要去差館報到等上庭<br />\n後尾好似係2條友和解左, 警察就撤銷左個charge<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過同樓主個case唔完全一樣...唔知有